Haskell worker, short instruction, later I will make cabal script for that.
Word_count compilation:
$ ghc --make Word_count.hs -o word_count

For sending package to disco -  I use jobpack written in Golang:

$ go get github.com/discoproject/goworker/jobpack
$ $GOPATH/bin/jobpack -W count_words -I http://discoproject.org/media/text/chekhov.txt

